Installation:

	git clone https://zdkroot@github.com/zdkroot/dotvim.git ~/.vim

	on windows clone into vim's install dir
        default is c:\program files\vim\vim73

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

	mklink /H C:/Program Files (x86)/Vim/_vimrc vim73\vimrc
	mklink /H C:/Program Files (x86)/Vim/_gvimrc vim73\gvimrc

Update config on new machine

	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update

Update plugins

	cd ~/.vim/bundle/fugitive
	git pull
